{"tid":1255860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 一人一post ] 626 朝早9點到夜晚9點！目標係G20 ! 一定要出！","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T13:38:57.000Z","uid":209679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2109c68a167dcaa04e234b7e7ea9fbdef0adb9d","tid":1255860,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"除左推人地626 既post, 大家可以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一人一post</span></span>推到<span style=\"color: orange;\">成頁都係626!</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(懶既直接係最底copy再開！) </span></div><br />\n<br />\n我知出黎太密係唔好，係攰，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但626係一撚定要出！指向G20! </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtL9TTM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtL9TTM.png&h=c54fd2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[香港本地]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6/26朝早9點</span></span>開始-野餐結束<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">日頭要多人，夜晚先會多人出！ </span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8eWQDmp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eWQDmp.png&h=c48e6ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAW1K1U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAW1K1U.png&h=5daa8179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42qU417.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42qU417.png&h=9c203f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmAU42L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmAU42L.png&h=9ef8f0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[海外集氣 - 澳洲_墨爾本]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6/26晏晝5點</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/379KHQE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F379KHQE.png&h=704e7a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6/27朝早10點</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tu2HuuM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTu2HuuM.png&h=3d0a789c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大家可以不同意，但記得不譴責！</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91tp44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91tp44.png&h=ff06b129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">拒絕分化、槍口一致<br />\n對準殺人政權<br />\n不退不讓！</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190624/s00001/1561345247367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190624%2Fs00001%2F1561345247367%2F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=5905eaa3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190624%2Fs00001%2F1561345247367%2F&h=9752b627\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190624/s00001/1561345247367/</a><br />\n【逃犯條例】外交部-中國不允許g20峰會討論香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張軍強調，港府修訂《逃犯條例》</span>[size=2]<span style=\"color: teal;\">等一系列舉措，是維護社會公義，彌補法律制度缺陷，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">是完全有必要的</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">，中央政府也會支持。</span></span>[/teal]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">張軍重申，香港是中國的特別行政區，</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港事務純屬中國內政，<span style=\"color: maroon;\">任何國家無權干預</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">口交部已經驚到出聲</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">各位香港人更加唔應該俾佢停<br />\n唔理用任何渠道都一定要draw多啲noise </div><br />\n令議會嘅事唔再局限喺立法會入面 而係連繫到香港街頭甚至海外<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">堅守底線，<br />\n因我們沒有退讓的理由。<br />\n<br />\n不撤不退！</div>"},{"pid":"eb9bdbf27ad42d2d39d1147afd7f39c7238bfbf8","tid":1255860,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T00:42:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1214fa3fdf35d26cfd234cb7e50427c4b0484272","tid":1255860,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}